### Liveness
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health/live
Accept: application/json

### Readiness
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health/ready
Accept: application/json

### Ingest one work item
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1/work-items
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "project_id": "DEMO",
    "workitem_id": "REQ-123",
    "title": "The system shall authenticate users",
    "text": "Users must authenticate before accessing protected resources.",
    "revision": 1,
    "status": "open",
    "linked_workitems": [],
    "custom_fields": {
      "workitem_type": "requirement",
      "priority": "high",
      "tags": ["security"]
    }
  }
]

### Semantic search, restricted to one project
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/v1/work-items/search?prompt=authentication&project_id=DEMO&limit=5
Accept: application/json
